I think its day.

::Prowl/Striker:;

Prowl nods. "Maybe its the same ship. Can you contact him?" he asks.

He looks at Lunarpine, "This is the Ark, an Autobot craft," he says, walking
off toward the bridge, "And I'm not in charge."

Outside the Ark, Striker turns around, remembering something. "Oh yeah," he
yells in Prowl's direction, "Iron Raptor left you in charge."

Prowl blinks. "I guess I am then," he says, continuing to walk to the 
bridge.
